        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Text-fig. 31. Aeduella blainvillei (AGASSIZ, 1833). A set of opercular and subopercular bones showing their variability. Scale bars 5 mm. a – left operculum in lateral view. MHK 82773. b – left operculum in lateral view. MHK 82775. c – left suboperculum in lateral view. MHK 82769. d – left suboperculum in lateral view. MHK 82786. e – left suboperculum in lateral view. G 3/1. f – left suboperculum in lateral view. G 3/1. g – right suboperculum in lateral view. BX 07.09.97. h – right suboperculum in lateral view. G 3/2." ;
